'''''Integration TV''''' waa barnaamij muuqbaahiye ah saldhiggiisu yahay dalka Kanada oo ay aasaastay [[Hodan Nalayeh]]. 

==Aragti guud==

[[File:Hodan_Nalayeh_Somalia.jpg|thumb|right|waa mid ka mid ah sawirada muujinaya silsilada ka mid barnaamijyo ay Hodan ku diyaarisay [[Muqadisho]], Soomaaliya]]
''Integration TV'' waxaa loo aqoonsaday muuqbaahiyhii ugu horeeyay ee afka Ingriisiga ku hadla ee [[Qurbajoogta soomaaliyeed]] sidoo kale waxa uu daboolaa in badan oo u baahi qabtay barnaamijyo ay daawadaan inta badan soomaalida, waxaa taa dheer dhacdooyinka bulshada soomaaliyeed ee dagan dalka kanada, fikradaha wawanaagsan ee [[Qurbajoogta Soomaaliyeed]] iyo dabagalka arrimaha ku saabsan horumarka Jamhuuriyadda Soomaaliya.

''Integration Television'' sidoo kale waxaa u hadaf ah isku xirka, bidhaaminta iyo xoojinta qurbajoogta Soomaaliyeed dhammaan caalamka.

Waxaa dheeraad ah soo saarista barnaamijyo todobaadle ah, bandhigyada qaybaha todobaadyada waxaa ka mid ah bedbedela sheekooyinka sida ''"Shaah & Sheeko"'' taasoo macnaheedu yahay "Tea and Talk" ee [[Af-Soomaaliga]]. ''Shaah & Sheeko'' ee lagu martigaliyo Soomaali kala duwan, waxaana looga doodaa qodobo muhim u ah bulshada Soomaaliyeed, waxaana kor loogu qaadaa wacyiga ku saabsan guud ahaan arrimaha bulshada.

''Integration Television'' waxaa laga soo daayaa dabayaaqada todobaad waliba FEVA TV iyadoo laga heli karo YouTube Channel.<ref>{{cite web|last1=FEVA TV|title=Integration TV|url=http://www.fevatv.com/integration/|accessdate=2 Oktoobar 2015|ciwaan=Nuqul Archive|archive-date=2015-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150629131328/http://www.fevatv.com/integration/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

===Martigaliyaha===

[[Hodan Nalayeh]] waa maamule warbaahineed, iskudubaride iyo wariye.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Nalayeh|first1=Hodan|title=Ms. Hodan Nalayeh (Executive Producer, Integration TV, As an Individual) at the Status of Women Committee|url=https://openparliament.ca/committees/status-of-women/41-2/35/hodan-nalayeh-1/only/|website=Open Parliament|publisher=Open North|accessdate=3 October 2015}}</ref> Hodan waxay ku dhalatay [[Laascaanood]], [[Soomaaliya]] sanaddii 1976 waxay u guurtay [[Edmonton]], [[Alberta]] sanaddii 1984. Hodan waxay heshay Bachelor kuna heshay fanka Tabinta ee [[Jaamacadda Windsor]].<ref>{{cite web|last1=Reason|first1=Cynthia|title=TV host Hodan Nalayeh shines a light on Somali life in Toronto|url=http://www.insidetoronto.com/news-story/4577505-tv-host-hodan-nalayeh-shines-a-light-on-somali-life-in-toronto/|website=Inside Toronto|publisher=2015 METROLAND MEDIA GROUP LTD|accessdate=4 October 2015}}</ref> Inta ayasn aasaasi Integration Television 2014, Hodan waxay noqtay qof sameeya soona saara barnaamijyo kala duwan iyo bandhigyo sifa ''So You Think You Can Dance Canada'' and ''American Idol''.

==Taariikh==

''Integration TV'' markuu ugu horaysay marso 2, 2014 ayuu ka baxay [[City TV]].<ref>{{cite web|last1=Hiiraan Online|title=Muuqbaahiye cusub oo soo bandhigaya sawirka Soomaali-Kanadiyaan in Mainstream Media!|url=http://www.hiiraan.ca/news4/2014/Feb/53415/new_television_show_uplifts_the_image_of_somali_canadians_in_mainstream_media.aspx|website=Hiraan Online}}</ref> Waqti soo horeeysay ee sanadkaan, waa laga joojiyay in lagu soo bandhigo [[City TV]] waxaana loo wareejiyay in lagu soo bandhigo [[YouTube]] channel.

Bishii May 28, 2015, Hodan waxay ku dhawaaqday in lahu soo bandhigi doono si todaadle ah FEVA TV.

==Martida==
[[Image:Integration Television Interview With Ontario Premier.png|thumb|right|''Integration Television'' [[Hodan Nalayeh]] oo la fadhisa [[Kathleen Wynne]] waraysina ka qaadaysa]]
Bandhigga waxaa ka soo muuqday marti caan ah kala si [[Kathleen Wynne]], wasiirka iskaashiga iyo xiriirka caalamiga ah Cabdi Caynte, sida atariishada dharka xayeesiisa ee [[Ayaan Cilmi]] iyo afhayeenka madaxa muslimiinta amerika [[Nouman Ali Khan]].

''Integration TV'' waxaa ka mid ah waxyaabaha uu soo gudbiyo barnaamij loogu talogalay horumarka Soomaaliya. Bishii Maajo 24, 2015, ''Integration TV'' waxaa caddeeyay 18-jir lagu magacaabo Rashid Cabdullahi deggan dalka [[Netherlands]] kaasoo soo bandhigay musalsal ''Integration TV'' lagu magacaabo "Muqdisho iyo xagaayga".<ref>{{cite web|last1=Nalayeh|first1=Hodan|title=INTEGRATION TV: waxaa loo ogolaaday in ay warbaahinta la hadasho! #My252Summer!|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eATLT383IZg|website=YouTube|publisher=Integration TV|accessdate=5 October 2015}}</ref> Bandhigga waxuu abaarayin uu iftiimiyo horumarka ka jira [[Muqadisho]], ee caasimadda [[Soomaaliya]]. Shan iyo toban silsiladood ee fadhi dhacdooyin ah oo ay ku jirto bandhigga buugaagta muqdisho ee caalamiga ah iyo dhandhigga dhaqanka [[Soomaaliyeed]].

==Hawlo biniaadamnimo iyo dhaqdhaqaaq bulsho==

''Integration TV'' maaha oo kaliya [[Warbaahin]]luugu talo galay Somali Canadians, waa mid dhammaan u furan bulshada. Bishii Juun 9, 2014, ururka gabdhaha Toronto ayaa ku dhawaaqay in ''Integration TV'' uu taabagaliayay.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Reason|first1=Cynthia|title=Young Somali soccer players find fun in fitness, learn soccer skills playing on girls-only team|url=http://www.insidetoronto.com/news-story/5639673-young-somali-soccer-players-find-fun-in-fitness-learn-soccer-skills-playing-on-girls-only-team/|website=Inside Toronto|publisher=METROLAND MEDIA GROUP LTD|accessdate=4 October 2015}}</ref> ''Integration TV'' sidoo kale wuxuu taaba galiyay 2015 Sanadlihii cuna dhaqameedka xalaasha ah oo fadhigooda ahaa
[[Mississauga, Ontario]].<ref>{{cite web|last1=Muslim Fest|title=Hodan Nalayeh|url=http://muslimfest.com/muslim_artists_friends/hodan-nalayeh/|website=Muslim Fest Mississauga|publisher=Muslim Fest|accessdate=4 October 2015}}</ref>

[[File:Hodan_Nalayeh_Soccer.jpg|thumb|right|Hodan iyo la sawiran tababaraha ururka gabdhaha cayaartooyda ee Toronto Hanan Warsame (midig) iyo qayb ka mid ah gabdhaha]]

In addition, ''Integration TV'' uses its influential platform to raise awareness for various causes. Nalayeh is the founder of the Somali Refugees Awareness Project, a non-profit organization that advocates for Somali refugees across the world and seeks to help protect and resettle refugees that fled Somalia during the 1990 civil war.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Keung|first1=Nicholas|title=Somali-Canadian youth seek solutions for their homeland|url=http://www.thestar.com/news/gta/2011/07/29/somalicanadian_youth_seek_solutions_for_their_homeland.html|website=Toronto Star|accessdate=6 October 2015}}</ref>

Sidoo kale, Integration TV wuxuu soo daaya barnaamij saamayn leh iyo iftiiminta horumarka qurbajoogta soomaaliyeed waana muasasad aan faaiida doon ahayn.  Bishii May 5, 2015, ''Integration TV'' wuxuu baahiyay wacyi galinta bulshada soomaaliyeed ee ku aadan xagga dhimirka ee Dr. Abdirahman Ali Habeeb, oo ah mid ku taqasusay caafimaadka xagga dhimirka asigoo xanaaneeya dad dhimirka la' ee [[Soomaaliya]]. asigoo kaashanaya [[Al Jazeera]], ''Integration TV'' shaagayna in uu taageerayo dhismaha xarun caafimaad ee laga dhiso mcaasimadda. Afar bil kadib, [[Madaxweynaha Soomaaliya]] wuxuu ku dhawaaqay in loogu deeqay dhul Dr. Xabeeb arrintiisii.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Nalayeh|first1=Hodan|title=Mental Health Doctor in Somalia! #DrHabebIsAHero|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iVf1T6_HvI8|website=YouTube|publisher=Integration TV|accessdate=5 October 2015}}</ref>

